snippet.title: Mortal Kombat X 4K/60fps PC Max Settings gameplay - MSI GTX 980 Gaming 4G
snippet.description:
!!!!! This is an 60 fps gameplay video!!!!!

We play the PC version of the Mortal Kombat X with Max Graphic Settings and at 4K resolution.
PC Specs
CPU: Intel Core i7 4790K @4.5Ghz
GPU: MSI GTX 980 Gaming 4G
Ram: 16GB DDR3 @1600MHz
Display: Samsung UD590 3840x2160

Enternity.gr YouTube channel: http://youtube.com/enternitygr

Αν το βίντεο σας άρεσε, εγγραφείτε στο κανάλι μας εδώ http://www.youtube.com/user/enternitygr?sub_confirmation=1.
